item.dc:creator: @mresi5656 mresi5656
item.description:
@mresi5656 wrote:

[quote=“Xbox Modder, post:5, topic:92911”]I am so sick and tired of thread in which 10 people post the same god damn thing… “Download Java!” “Have Java” “Here, download java!”

It’s so friggin’ annoying…

Also, a “gray” screen has nothing to do with the version of java… It has to do with his available RAM and the amount of paging file he is using… If he’s running his server and trying to load moparscape or compiling while trying to load it yea… Your going to get a gray screen because it doesn;t have the virtual memory to show the graphics of that area… Well, refresh that area so the FPS is probably 2-3 until they free up virtual memory…

Seriously, don;t post unless you know what your talking about…[/quote]

Wow… I’m sorry. Seriously.
